problem points if you do that.

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:47.380
We do a lot of pre-planning.

00:08:47.510 --> 00:08:48.440
We go through.

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.440
We take pictures of all
the different areas.

00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:54.420
We then put together
storyboards for video work.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:57.250
We put together real storyboards,
and we get the clients to

00:08:57.250 --> 00:08:58.440
sign off on the storyboards.

